high_descs: Stand up turn around walk towards the bed.
Pick up the pillow from the bed.
Turn around walk towards the side table.
Keep the pillow on the top of the side table.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the pillow from the bed and keep it on the top of the side table.

high_descs: Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the bed.
Pick up pillow from the bed.
Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the side table.
Place pillow on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Shifting pillow from one place to another.

high_descs: Head right to reach the bedroom and turn left to face the bed.
Pick up the pillow at the back of the bed.
Turn around to reach the side table.
Put the pillow on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Put the pillow on the side table.
